(en) Irrationality was chased out of the church, \nbut religion returned here, in a wilder, \nmore primitive form.
On a chassé l'irrationalité de l'église,\nmais la religion est revenue ici, \nsous une forme plus sauvage, plus primitive.
(en) What did we do wrong?\nHaven't we educated people enough?
